00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
<font color="yellow">(Viewer discretion is advised.)</font>

3
00:00:24,840 --> 00:00:26,610
<font color="yellow">Did you break up with Dong Jin?</font>

4
00:00:27,670 --> 00:00:30,440
<font color="yellow">We didn't have to break up.</font>

5
00:00:30,640 --> 00:00:35,610
<font color="yellow">Why did you date Dong Jin when you left Yeon Ha?</font>

6
00:00:36,140 --> 00:00:37,140
<font color="yellow">Mum.</font>

7
00:00:38,070 --> 00:00:39,710
<font color="yellow">I'm here to interview you.</font>

8
00:00:41,440 --> 00:00:42,470
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

9
00:00:44,010 --> 00:00:45,470
<font color="yellow">Your wish was...</font>

10
00:00:45,770 --> 00:00:47,010
<font color="yellow">for me to write a novel...</font>

11
00:00:47,510 --> 00:00:49,110
<font color="yellow">about you and your friends.</font>

12
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:51,370
<font color="yellow">So I'm here to interview you.</font>

13
00:00:51,370 --> 00:00:53,740
<font color="yellow">Why did you break up with Yeon Ha?</font>

14
00:00:54,640 --> 00:00:55,810
<font color="yellow">Did you like him?</font>

15
00:00:56,270 --> 00:00:57,540
<font color="yellow">Did you date him?</font>

16
00:01:01,840 --> 00:01:05,070
<font color="yellow">Where should we begin?</font>

17
00:01:05,440 --> 00:01:07,140
<font color="yellow">When you were born?</font>

18
00:01:07,670 --> 00:01:10,740
<font color="yellow">Or around your earliest memories?</font>

19
00:01:12,270 --> 00:01:13,440
<font color="yellow">Should we start there?</font>

20
00:01:13,740 --> 00:01:15,640
<font color="yellow">You dated him, didn't you?</font>

21
00:01:16,110 --> 00:01:18,340
<font color="yellow">I'm pretty sure you did.</font>

22
00:01:18,640 --> 00:01:21,070
<font color="yellow">Why did you break up?</font>

23
00:01:22,010 --> 00:01:24,240
<font color="yellow">Did he cheat on you?</font>

24
00:01:24,310 --> 00:01:25,840
<font color="yellow">Like Dong Jin did?</font>

25
00:01:28,910 --> 00:01:30,270
<font color="yellow">He's disabled.</font>

26
00:01:33,940 --> 00:01:36,510
<font color="yellow">You told me not to marry a disabled man.</font>

27
00:01:40,310 --> 00:01:41,710
<font color="yellow">So we broke up.</font>

28
00:01:43,640 --> 00:01:45,710
<font color="yellow">No, I pretty much threw him away.</font>

29
00:01:46,740 --> 00:01:48,210
<font color="yellow">I'm that obedient.</font>

30
00:01:52,270 --> 00:01:55,010
<font color="yellow">Shall we begin the interview?</font>

31
00:01:56,040 --> 00:01:57,240
<font color="yellow">How about this?</font>

32
00:02:00,340 --> 00:02:03,110
<font color="yellow">Your story should begin...</font>

33
00:02:03,570 --> 00:02:06,110
<font color="yellow">when we visited Grandma when I was six.</font>

34
00:02:06,110 --> 00:02:07,110
<font color="yellow">Let's start there.</font>

35
00:02:14,140 --> 00:02:15,140
<font color="yellow">Don't you remember?</font>

36
00:02:16,670 --> 00:02:18,810
<font color="yellow">I remember it so clearly.</font>

37
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:21,240
<font color="yellow">Mum.</font>

38
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:23,610
<font color="yellow">Why did you try to kill me?</font>

39
00:02:38,670 --> 00:02:41,210
<font color="yellow">Don't you remember? In the field.</font>

40
00:02:52,010 --> 00:02:53,370
<font color="yellow">What field?</font>

41
00:02:55,140 --> 00:02:56,140
<font color="yellow">What...</font>

42
00:02:56,540 --> 00:02:58,940
<font color="yellow">No... Have you lost your mind?</font>

43
00:03:00,140 --> 00:03:02,910
<font color="yellow">What nonsense are you talking about?</font>

44
00:03:02,910 --> 00:03:05,310
<font color="yellow">Did you really not date Dong Jin?</font>

45
00:03:05,310 --> 00:03:06,710
<font color="yellow">Then why did he kiss you?</font>

46
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:08,040
<font color="yellow">Why did you hug?</font>

47
00:03:08,270 --> 00:03:10,840
<font color="yellow">No woman in her right mind would hug a married man.</font>

48
00:03:10,940 --> 00:03:13,310
<font color="yellow">Don't you dare like to me.</font>

49
00:03:13,540 --> 00:03:15,540
<font color="yellow">- That was a mistake. - A mistake?</font>

50
00:03:15,770 --> 00:03:17,170
<font color="yellow">That's an excuse.</font>

51
00:03:17,270 --> 00:03:19,340
<font color="yellow">Were you obedient?</font>

52
00:03:19,370 --> 00:03:21,740
<font color="yellow">Were you so obedient that you...</font>

53
00:03:21,740 --> 00:03:24,010
<font color="yellow">decided to play the other woman?</font>

54
00:03:24,110 --> 00:03:25,740
<font color="yellow">What a joke.</font>

55
00:03:26,210 --> 00:03:27,210
<font color="yellow">I'll wait.</font>

56
00:03:27,210 --> 00:03:30,670
<font color="yellow">I mean less to you than dog poop on the street!</font>

57
00:03:30,940 --> 00:03:34,210
<font color="yellow">How could you when you know what your dad did to me!</font>

58
00:03:34,740 --> 00:03:37,170
<font color="yellow">What? It was a mistake?</font>

59
00:03:37,570 --> 00:03:40,740
<font color="yellow">How dare you say such a thing?</font>

60
00:03:56,870 --> 00:03:58,440
<font color="yellow">Welcome.</font>

61
00:03:58,440 --> 00:03:59,440
<font color="yellow">- Hey. - Yes?</font>

62
00:03:59,440 --> 00:04:00,810
<font color="yellow">Clean the tables inside.</font>

63
00:04:00,810 --> 00:04:02,010
<font color="yellow">- We have new customers. - Okay.</font>

64
00:04:02,010 --> 00:04:04,140
<font color="yellow">- A tangsuyuk and three jjamppongs? - Yes.</font>

65
00:04:05,270 --> 00:04:09,110
<font color="yellow">How dare she stiffen her neck at me?</font>

66
00:04:09,110 --> 00:04:11,640
<font color="yellow">I'm her mother.</font>

67
00:04:11,640 --> 00:04:14,940
<font color="yellow">Where did she learn to give me a look like that?</font>

68
00:04:15,210 --> 00:04:18,110
<font color="yellow">I shouldn't be so lenient with her.</font>

69
00:04:18,770 --> 00:04:20,680
<font color="yellow">- That's hot. - Gosh.</font>

70
00:04:25,740 --> 00:04:27,040
<font color="yellow">Put ice on it.</font>

71
00:04:28,940 --> 00:04:31,710
<font color="yellow">We have a group of 30 coming in tonight.</font>

72
00:04:31,810 --> 00:04:34,410
<font color="yellow">Give them a lot of free dishes. I'm going home.</font>

73
00:04:36,110 --> 00:04:38,040
<font color="yellow">I told you I'd fry them.</font>

74
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:43,140
<font color="yellow">- We're on our own tonight. - It's going to be crazy.</font>

75
00:04:43,470 --> 00:04:44,870
<font color="yellow">Work if you have time to chat.</font>

76
00:04:45,370 --> 00:04:46,570
<font color="yellow">Goodness.</font>

77
00:04:51,310 --> 00:04:52,310
<font color="yellow">That's tasty.</font>

78
00:04:57,470 --> 00:04:59,340
<font color="yellow">"Ma'am, it's Dong Jin."</font>

79
00:04:59,340 --> 00:05:03,840
<font color="yellow">"It's a misunderstanding. Wan and I are not what you think."</font>

80
00:05:04,180 --> 00:05:05,510
<font color="yellow">"We're not..."</font>

81
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,410
<font color="yellow">What a lie.</font>

82
00:05:07,740 --> 00:05:09,810
<font color="yellow">Can't he make up his mind?</font>

83
00:05:09,940 --> 00:05:12,340
<font color="yellow">He's going to leave for United States with his wife soon.</font>

84
00:05:12,410 --> 00:05:15,140
<font color="yellow">I should just kick him again.</font>

85
00:05:17,740 --> 00:05:19,680
<font color="yellow">Do you sell these in single bags?</font>

86
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:20,770
<font color="yellow">I just want one bag.</font>

87
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:24,180
<font color="yellow">I just asked you a question.</font>

88
00:05:24,180 --> 00:05:25,180
<font color="yellow">Do you or do you not?</font>

89
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:27,070
<font color="yellow">We only sell them in packages...</font>

90
00:05:28,610 --> 00:05:30,970
<font color="yellow">Why are you rude to me?</font>

91
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:33,410
<font color="yellow">You were rude to her first.</font>

92
00:05:38,610 --> 00:05:39,640
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

93
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:47,140
<font color="yellow">Goodness. It's just a little bit further.</font>

94
00:05:49,510 --> 00:05:51,040
<font color="yellow">Jeong A.</font>

95
00:05:52,740 --> 00:05:53,940
<font color="yellow">Jeong A.</font>

96
00:05:54,770 --> 00:05:57,770
<font color="yellow">Why did you tag along? Just go to church.</font>

97
00:05:58,110 --> 00:05:59,840
<font color="yellow">She's so annoying.</font>

98
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:10,910
<font color="yellow">Jeong A.</font>

99
00:06:13,470 --> 00:06:17,340
<font color="yellow">(Dear My Friends, Isn't Life So Beautiful?)</font>

100
00:06:19,440 --> 00:06:21,240
<font color="yellow">Here.</font>

101
00:06:21,610 --> 00:06:22,740
<font color="yellow">Oh, my.</font>

102
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:25,470
<font color="yellow">There will be ghosts here.</font>

103
00:06:25,910 --> 00:06:27,010
<font color="yellow">It has a good view.</font>

104
00:06:27,770 --> 00:06:32,010
<font color="yellow">Of course. We walked up the mountain for 30 minutes.</font>

105
00:06:32,310 --> 00:06:34,010
<font color="yellow">You're too old to walk up.</font>

106
00:06:34,370 --> 00:06:36,210
<font color="yellow">Come on. It'll be good exercise.</font>

107
00:06:36,440 --> 00:06:37,810
<font color="yellow">The bus comes up this way.</font>

108
00:06:40,870 --> 00:06:42,270
<font color="yellow">The water pressure is good.</font>

109
00:06:42,270 --> 00:06:43,770
<font color="yellow">No, don't get this place.</font>

110
00:06:44,010 --> 00:06:47,070
<font color="yellow">It's further from me than my kids in the Philippines.</font>

111
00:06:47,440 --> 00:06:49,470
<font color="yellow">I could ride on cars and planes to get there,</font>

112
00:06:50,110 --> 00:06:51,110
<font color="yellow">but here...</font>

113
00:06:51,110 --> 00:06:53,940
<font color="yellow">You asked me to find a place in your neighbourhood.</font>

114
00:06:54,140 --> 00:06:56,810
<font color="yellow">That's why I'm looking at this place.</font>

115
00:06:57,070 --> 00:06:59,010
<font color="yellow">Also, the Philippines is further than here.</font>

116
00:06:59,210 --> 00:07:02,040
<font color="yellow">Why do you only look at the bad things? I like it here.</font>

117
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:03,210
<font color="yellow">I can't allow you to get this place.</font>

118
00:07:03,640 --> 00:07:05,610
<font color="yellow">Sir, can you show us somewhere else?</font>

119
00:07:06,410 --> 00:07:07,410
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

120
00:07:09,610 --> 00:07:10,940
<font color="yellow">Wait, I have to put my shoes on.</font>

121
00:07:11,810 --> 00:07:13,610
<font color="yellow">No, not this place either.</font>

122
00:07:15,310 --> 00:07:18,410
<font color="yellow">This is a really good deal for 50,000 dollars.</font>

123
00:07:19,370 --> 00:07:22,610
<font color="yellow">If it's that good, you should live here. I'll pass.</font>

124
00:07:22,740 --> 00:07:24,640
<font color="yellow">You're not living here. Where are you going?</font>

125
00:07:26,140 --> 00:07:28,070
<font color="yellow">Just live with me.</font>

126
00:07:28,070 --> 00:07:31,340
<font color="yellow">Go home and stop getting in my way.</font>

127
00:07:33,910 --> 00:07:35,270
<font color="yellow">Gosh.</font>

128
00:07:36,770 --> 00:07:40,240
<font color="yellow">I can't show you any more! That's all I have!</font>

129
00:07:40,540 --> 00:07:41,910
<font color="yellow">Goodness...</font>

130
00:07:42,670 --> 00:07:44,840
<font color="yellow">This looks tasteful.</font>

131
00:07:45,410 --> 00:07:47,740
<font color="yellow">I used to live in a place like this when I got married.</font>

132
00:07:49,070 --> 00:07:51,610
<font color="yellow">But you're not a mole. A basement house?</font>

133
00:07:51,740 --> 00:07:53,110
<font color="yellow">Will it be too dark?</font>

134
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:55,270
<font color="yellow">You need sunlight when you're old.</font>

135
00:07:55,270 --> 00:07:57,410
<font color="yellow">You'll get osteoporosis and depression.</font>

136
00:07:58,370 --> 00:08:00,540
<font color="yellow">That's true, I need some sun...</font>

137
00:08:04,340 --> 00:08:05,340
<font color="yellow">What is it?</font>

138
00:08:05,340 --> 00:08:08,140
<font color="yellow">Pollack soup. Put in a lot of pepper powder.</font>

139
00:08:08,970 --> 00:08:11,370
<font color="yellow">Sir. Can you help me?</font>

140
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:16,240
<font color="yellow">Here.</font>

141
00:08:16,870 --> 00:08:18,940
<font color="yellow">Not this one. That small one.</font>

142
00:08:28,410 --> 00:08:29,440
<font color="yellow">What's that?</font>

143
00:08:29,440 --> 00:08:30,440
<font color="yellow">Toilet paper.</font>

144
00:08:30,870 --> 00:08:31,870
<font color="yellow">What is this?</font>

145
00:08:31,940 --> 00:08:34,110
<font color="yellow">Bricks for decoration.</font>

146
00:08:37,510 --> 00:08:39,740
<font color="yellow">I hope you get hit by lightning.</font>

147
00:08:42,410 --> 00:08:43,570
<font color="yellow">What did Seok Gyun say?</font>

148
00:08:43,640 --> 00:08:45,010
<font color="yellow">He wants pollack soup.</font>

149
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:47,640
<font color="yellow">What's all this noise? Go away.</font>

150
00:08:54,710 --> 00:08:58,170
<font color="yellow">I haven't been yelled at in a while.</font>

151
00:08:58,870 --> 00:09:00,240
<font color="yellow">You had a peaceful life.</font>

152
00:09:00,310 --> 00:09:01,370
<font color="yellow">Where are you going?</font>

153
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,470
<font color="yellow">To buy pollack.</font>

154
00:09:04,870 --> 00:09:07,470
<font color="yellow">When are you going to get the divorce?</font>

155
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:09,140
<font color="yellow">After I get a place.</font>

156
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:12,510
<font color="yellow">Don't make him the soup or don't get a divorce.</font>

157
00:09:12,780 --> 00:09:14,510
<font color="yellow">You're so strange.</font>

158
00:09:15,040 --> 00:09:18,710
<font color="yellow">You should talk to him before moving out.</font>

159
00:09:18,710 --> 00:09:20,780
<font color="yellow">You'll shock him if you do this so suddenly.</font>

160
00:09:20,780 --> 00:09:22,310
<font color="yellow">Let him get a shock.</font>

161
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:25,070
<font color="yellow">It won't change anything even if I do. It'll just be noisy.</font>

162
00:09:26,010 --> 00:09:29,410
<font color="yellow">Did you tell the kids? They'll get shocked, too.</font>

163
00:09:29,410 --> 00:09:31,870
<font color="yellow">I liked the first house.</font>

164
00:09:32,540 --> 00:09:34,940
<font color="yellow">You should go. I'm going to take a look at it again.</font>

165
00:09:37,540 --> 00:09:40,010
<font color="yellow">I'll wait for you at the three-way with the pollack.</font>

166
00:09:40,340 --> 00:09:41,940
<font color="yellow">I think you could see Han River.</font>

167
00:10:03,110 --> 00:10:05,940
<font color="yellow">Mum, why did you try to kill me?</font>

168
00:10:43,070 --> 00:10:44,140
<font color="yellow">Choong Nam.</font>

169
00:10:45,570 --> 00:10:47,510
<font color="yellow">Hey, Joo Yeong. Where's your aunt?</font>

170
00:10:49,570 --> 00:10:52,280
<font color="yellow">Professor Yang, you're really making masterpieces these days.</font>

171
00:10:52,280 --> 00:10:55,440
<font color="yellow">There are a million stories for each photograph.</font>

172
00:10:55,940 --> 00:10:58,110
<font color="yellow">I would buy all of it if I had the money.</font>

173
00:10:58,110 --> 00:10:59,870
<font color="yellow">Do you want to sell it to me for half the price?</font>

174
00:10:59,870 --> 00:11:03,940
<font color="yellow">Stop it. Poverty is what made me who I am today.</font>

175
00:11:04,210 --> 00:11:06,640
<font color="yellow">Poverty for an artist isn't a flaw.</font>

176
00:11:06,640 --> 00:11:10,840
<font color="yellow">I agree. People don't have such a philosophy any more.</font>

177
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:13,240
<font color="yellow">All they care about is money.</font>

178
00:11:13,610 --> 00:11:18,070
<font color="yellow">These pictures are really great.</font>

179
00:11:18,070 --> 00:11:20,510
<font color="yellow">If I had bidders,</font>

180
00:11:20,940 --> 00:11:23,710
<font color="yellow">I would have bought that vase from you.</font>

181
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:27,940
<font color="yellow">It's Nan Hee.</font>

182
00:11:28,110 --> 00:11:29,840
<font color="yellow">If it isn't about life or death, tell her to call later.</font>

183
00:11:32,940 --> 00:11:36,640
<font color="yellow">She says you should call back unless it's about life or death.</font>

184
00:11:36,770 --> 00:11:38,370
<font color="yellow">Her young professor friends are over.</font>

185
00:11:38,610 --> 00:11:40,670
<font color="yellow">I guess she's less interested in her old friends.</font>

186
00:11:40,670 --> 00:11:41,670
<font color="yellow">Hey!</font>

187
00:11:41,740 --> 00:11:43,810
<font color="yellow">It's not about life or death,</font>

188
00:11:44,040 --> 00:11:47,440
<font color="yellow">but tell her that old friends are important, too.</font>

189
00:11:52,040 --> 00:11:53,040
<font color="yellow">(Yeong Won)</font>

190
00:11:56,040 --> 00:11:57,070
<font color="yellow">Hey, Nan Hee.</font>

191
00:11:57,640 --> 00:11:58,870
<font color="yellow">Buy me a drink.</font>

192
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:01,770
<font color="yellow">I can't, I'm shooting.</font>

193
00:12:02,740 --> 00:12:04,270
<font color="yellow">Can we drink tomorrow?</font>

194
00:12:04,940 --> 00:12:06,940
<font color="yellow">Ma'am. Over there...</font>

195
00:12:13,940 --> 00:12:16,540
<font color="yellow">I'm not off every day. Go back to work then.</font>

196
00:12:22,870 --> 00:12:25,870
<font color="yellow">Why is she doing laundry? She should go home.</font>

197
00:12:28,610 --> 00:12:30,440
<font color="yellow">Yeon Ha was perfect.</font>

198
00:12:43,940 --> 00:12:46,810
<font color="yellow">Where did she go? She said she would wait here.</font>

199
00:12:47,540 --> 00:12:49,610
<font color="yellow">Did she buy the pollack or not?</font>

200
00:12:53,310 --> 00:12:55,140
<font color="yellow">You look like garden cosmos.</font>

201
00:13:04,810 --> 00:13:06,840
<font color="yellow">Where did you come from?</font>

202
00:13:07,170 --> 00:13:08,270
<font color="yellow">Where is your mum?</font>

203
00:13:09,540 --> 00:13:13,470
<font color="yellow">Come here, come here.</font>

204
00:13:14,410 --> 00:13:17,170
<font color="yellow">Try and catch me.</font>

205
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:22,340
<font color="yellow">Where are you going?</font>

206
00:13:23,670 --> 00:13:27,240
<font color="yellow">How are you going to wait for me here?</font>

207
00:13:27,240 --> 00:13:28,970
<font color="yellow">I'll be shooting until late.</font>

208
00:13:29,270 --> 00:13:31,540
<font color="yellow">Get up and wait in the car. Come on.</font>

209
00:13:31,970 --> 00:13:33,310
<font color="yellow">No, it's too stuffy.</font>

210
00:13:33,440 --> 00:13:34,640
<font color="yellow">Come on.</font>

211
00:13:34,670 --> 00:13:36,540
<font color="yellow">Ma'am, we're shooting!</font>

212
00:13:37,040 --> 00:13:38,310
<font color="yellow">Coming.</font>

213
00:13:39,170 --> 00:13:40,640
<font color="yellow">Go to the car.</font>

214
00:13:41,210 --> 00:13:42,810
<font color="yellow">Gosh, you're so stubborn.</font>

215
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:45,870
<font color="yellow">Don't you know it's annoying to be an old, stubborn person?</font>

216
00:13:48,410 --> 00:13:49,610
<font color="yellow">- Hey. - Yes.</font>

217
00:13:50,470 --> 00:13:53,070
<font color="yellow">- Get her a chair and a drink, okay? - Okay.</font>

218
00:13:54,540 --> 00:13:55,610
<font color="yellow">Gosh.</font>

219
00:14:14,270 --> 00:14:15,270
<font color="yellow">Where are you?</font>

220
00:14:15,370 --> 00:14:16,370
<font color="yellow">I'm off to see Mum.</font>

221
00:14:17,070 --> 00:14:19,610
<font color="yellow">Why go there when you know I'm waiting for you?</font>

222
00:14:19,710 --> 00:14:22,810
<font color="yellow">I go wherever I want to regardless of where you are.</font>

223
00:14:22,870 --> 00:14:25,540
<font color="yellow">Do I need your permission to see my mum?</font>

224
00:14:25,640 --> 00:14:27,510
<font color="yellow">Since when did you care about me?</font>

225
00:14:55,040 --> 00:14:56,040
<font color="yellow">Seong Jae?</font>

226
00:14:56,810 --> 00:14:58,140
<font color="yellow">Jeong A.</font>

227
00:14:58,270 --> 00:14:59,270
<font color="yellow">Is Hee Ja out?</font>

228
00:14:59,340 --> 00:15:01,710
<font color="yellow">No, but she won't let me in.</font>

229
00:15:01,910 --> 00:15:03,740
<font color="yellow">What's wrong with her?</font>

230
00:15:03,810 --> 00:15:05,910
<font color="yellow">She can't keep a visitor waiting.</font>

231
00:15:38,910 --> 00:15:41,370
<font color="yellow">- Why are you here? - Why do you think?</font>

232
00:15:42,240 --> 00:15:45,640
<font color="yellow">You said you'd buy frozen pollack and wait at the three-way.</font>

233
00:15:46,240 --> 00:15:47,240
<font color="yellow">Oh dear.</font>

234
00:15:47,310 --> 00:15:50,610
<font color="yellow">"Oh dear"? You let your mind wander.</font>

235
00:15:51,310 --> 00:15:54,310
<font color="yellow">- Where's the fish? - I bought that.</font>

236
00:15:58,940 --> 00:15:59,940
<font color="yellow">Here.</font>

237
00:16:00,810 --> 00:16:02,370
<font color="yellow">On the way back,</font>

238
00:16:02,470 --> 00:16:04,470
<font color="yellow">I noticed some flowers by the road.</font>

239
00:16:05,510 --> 00:16:08,340
<font color="yellow">Then I saw a lost little puppy.</font>

240
00:16:09,810 --> 00:16:13,240
<font color="yellow">It was this big. I followed it and ended up at home.</font>

241
00:16:14,240 --> 00:16:16,770
<font color="yellow">I couldn't remember why I'd bought the fish.</font>

242
00:16:16,870 --> 00:16:19,770
<font color="yellow">Do you know how scary it is when someone disappears?</font>

243
00:16:20,610 --> 00:16:21,740
<font color="yellow">Why didn't you answer your phone?</font>

244
00:16:21,870 --> 00:16:23,270
<font color="yellow">Is the battery flat?</font>

245
00:16:23,370 --> 00:16:25,510
<font color="yellow">Keep a spare battery and your mind on you.</font>

246
00:16:26,040 --> 00:16:27,040
<font color="yellow">Who am I?</font>

247
00:16:28,010 --> 00:16:29,010
<font color="yellow">Jeong A.</font>

248
00:16:29,110 --> 00:16:30,510
<font color="yellow">You're fine now.</font>

249
00:16:31,540 --> 00:16:33,340
<font color="yellow">Why didn't you let Seong Jae in?</font>

250
00:16:35,510 --> 00:16:36,510
<font color="yellow">Choong Nam.</font>

251
00:16:40,170 --> 00:16:41,440
<font color="yellow">Bye, Seong Jae.</font>

252
00:16:42,170 --> 00:16:43,610
<font color="yellow">See you soon.</font>

253
00:16:45,440 --> 00:16:46,710
<font color="yellow">Wake up.</font>

254
00:16:52,910 --> 00:16:53,970
<font color="yellow">Go home.</font>

255
00:17:15,510 --> 00:17:16,640
<font color="yellow">Why did you do that?</font>

256
00:17:17,070 --> 00:17:18,540
<font color="yellow">Why film me?</font>

257
00:17:18,840 --> 00:17:22,610
<font color="yellow">Point it at the door to see if a stranger comes in.</font>

258
00:17:27,570 --> 00:17:29,910
<font color="yellow">Take these and put the rosaries in a bag.</font>

259
00:17:32,010 --> 00:17:33,540
<font color="yellow">The priest sent me.</font>

260
00:17:33,770 --> 00:17:36,270
<font color="yellow">I didn't feel comfortable coming here,</font>

261
00:17:36,510 --> 00:17:39,440
<font color="yellow">but our priest told me to check on you...</font>

262
00:17:40,070 --> 00:17:42,340
<font color="yellow">and collect the rosaries you made.</font>

263
00:17:42,740 --> 00:17:45,670
<font color="yellow">Apparently, some old people sell them and keep the money.</font>

264
00:17:46,010 --> 00:17:47,010
<font color="yellow">I have to bring them.</font>

265
00:17:51,010 --> 00:17:52,870
<font color="yellow">Are there 100?</font>

266
00:17:54,240 --> 00:17:56,340
<font color="yellow">- I'll count them. - Don't bother.</font>

267
00:17:56,440 --> 00:17:57,910
<font color="yellow">You don't have to.</font>

268
00:17:58,910 --> 00:17:59,910
<font color="yellow">It's fine.</font>

269
00:18:16,070 --> 00:18:17,070
<font color="yellow">Do you like...</font>

270
00:18:17,440 --> 00:18:18,440
<font color="yellow">not smiling...</font>

271
00:18:19,110 --> 00:18:21,370
<font color="yellow">and saying the bare minimum as if we're strangers?</font>

272
00:18:21,810 --> 00:18:22,940
<font color="yellow">If I were to leave,</font>

273
00:18:23,670 --> 00:18:26,010
<font color="yellow">would that make you feel better?</font>

274
00:18:27,110 --> 00:18:28,340
<font color="yellow">I'd feel less uncomfortable.</font>

275
00:18:29,740 --> 00:18:31,040
<font color="yellow">Did I ask you to move in?</font>

276
00:18:32,110 --> 00:18:33,810
<font color="yellow">Let's have fun. Not as a date.</font>

277
00:18:34,340 --> 00:18:35,340
<font color="yellow">As friends.</font>

278
00:18:35,810 --> 00:18:37,770
<font color="yellow">Rather than stay indoors all day,</font>

279
00:18:37,870 --> 00:18:40,410
<font color="yellow">wouldn't it be nice to join me for a drive?</font>

280
00:18:40,710 --> 00:18:42,110
<font color="yellow">And enjoy the sun?</font>

281
00:18:42,210 --> 00:18:43,810
<font color="yellow">Jeong A can drive, too.</font>

282
00:18:44,440 --> 00:18:46,710
<font color="yellow">We go out for a drive sometimes.</font>

283
00:18:46,810 --> 00:18:48,840
<font color="yellow">You always have the last word.</font>

284
00:18:50,140 --> 00:18:51,740
<font color="yellow">I give up.</font>

285
00:19:00,510 --> 00:19:01,510
<font color="yellow">Wait.</font>

286
00:19:01,870 --> 00:19:04,240
<font color="yellow">Did I give Jeong A the fish?</font>

287
00:19:12,550 --> 00:19:13,620
<font color="yellow">I'm starving.</font>

288
00:19:17,790 --> 00:19:18,790
<font color="yellow">Thanks.</font>

289
00:19:25,490 --> 00:19:26,760
<font color="yellow">This old man...</font>

290
00:19:31,720 --> 00:19:33,050
<font color="yellow">He's her friend.</font>

291
00:19:33,220 --> 00:19:34,390
<font color="yellow">And Jeong A's there.</font>

292
00:19:34,790 --> 00:19:37,760
<font color="yellow">It's for the better. Seeing her alone upset you.</font>

293
00:19:37,890 --> 00:19:41,450
<font color="yellow">Now, you just have to worry when the door doesn't open...</font>

294
00:19:41,520 --> 00:19:42,720
<font color="yellow">for a whole day.</font>

295
00:19:45,220 --> 00:19:46,220
<font color="yellow">Who comes first?</font>

296
00:19:46,790 --> 00:19:48,350
<font color="yellow">Me or your mum?</font>

297
00:19:49,490 --> 00:19:50,490
<font color="yellow">You, then Mum.</font>

298
00:19:50,550 --> 00:19:51,550
<font color="yellow">And when our baby's here?</font>

299
00:19:52,150 --> 00:19:53,950
<font color="yellow">You, Mum and the baby.</font>

300
00:19:54,050 --> 00:19:56,490
<font color="yellow">I'll kill you if you put the baby before me.</font>

301
00:19:56,590 --> 00:19:58,320
<font color="yellow">That will only spoil the kid.</font>

302
00:19:58,420 --> 00:19:59,420
<font color="yellow">My mum said so.</font>

303
00:20:01,290 --> 00:20:02,290
<font color="yellow">You mentioned her again!</font>

304
00:20:11,220 --> 00:20:12,450
<font color="yellow">- Won't you eat? - No.</font>

305
00:20:14,350 --> 00:20:15,390
<font color="yellow">It's beef.</font>

306
00:20:16,020 --> 00:20:17,420
<font color="yellow">Have some.</font>

307
00:20:17,520 --> 00:20:19,390
<font color="yellow">It's sirloin. It's nice and tender.</font>

308
00:20:22,820 --> 00:20:23,820
<font color="yellow">What a jerk.</font>

309
00:20:24,650 --> 00:20:27,260
<font color="yellow">Where are his manners?</font>

310
00:20:27,690 --> 00:20:29,590
<font color="yellow">I have to go to the market early!</font>

311
00:20:29,690 --> 00:20:31,690
<font color="yellow">Eat and let me do the dishes.</font>

312
00:20:32,050 --> 00:20:33,390
<font color="yellow">What a fool.</font>

313
00:20:35,450 --> 00:20:37,720
<font color="yellow">Chew slowly and carefully.</font>

314
00:20:37,820 --> 00:20:39,720
<font color="yellow">You don't want to choke.</font>

315
00:20:42,950 --> 00:20:44,920
<font color="yellow">Cough harder.</font>

316
00:21:08,590 --> 00:21:10,250
<font color="yellow">You have a working toilet at home.</font>

317
00:21:11,450 --> 00:21:13,090
<font color="yellow">At least something still works.</font>

318
00:21:13,190 --> 00:21:15,250
<font color="yellow">Do you think I'm not man enough?</font>

319
00:21:15,350 --> 00:21:17,150
<font color="yellow">It was a concern.</font>

320
00:21:17,350 --> 00:21:18,920
<font color="yellow">You could ruin a woman's life.</font>

321
00:21:19,020 --> 00:21:21,990
<font color="yellow">Not so long ago, you couldn't even move.</font>

322
00:21:22,520 --> 00:21:23,620
<font color="yellow">You only started walking...</font>

323
00:21:23,720 --> 00:21:26,390
<font color="yellow">2, 3 years ago after spending 7 years in bed.</font>

324
00:21:26,650 --> 00:21:29,750
<font color="yellow">Jacqueline might not like you.</font>

325
00:21:29,850 --> 00:21:31,850
<font color="yellow">What if you spend 20,000 on her and she runs away?</font>

326
00:21:32,220 --> 00:21:35,020
<font color="yellow">Isn't that what happened to one of your neighbours?</font>

327
00:21:35,620 --> 00:21:37,620
<font color="yellow">You can't buy a woman's love.</font>

328
00:21:38,650 --> 00:21:41,090
<font color="yellow">Jacqueline likes me, too.</font>

329
00:21:41,590 --> 00:21:43,820
<font color="yellow">I may be disabled, but I farm,</font>

330
00:21:43,920 --> 00:21:45,650
<font color="yellow">chop wood and plow fields!</font>

331
00:21:46,790 --> 00:21:49,890
<font color="yellow">What? Can't a disabled man fall in love?</font>

332
00:21:55,020 --> 00:21:56,050
<font color="yellow">In Bong.</font>

333
00:21:57,150 --> 00:21:58,390
<font color="yellow">He's disabled.</font>

334
00:21:59,720 --> 00:22:02,250
<font color="yellow">You told me not to marry a disabled man.</font>

335
00:22:05,220 --> 00:22:06,650
<font color="yellow">So we broke up.</font>

336
00:22:08,590 --> 00:22:10,420
<font color="yellow">No, I pretty much threw him away.</font>

337
00:22:11,650 --> 00:22:12,920
<font color="yellow">I'm that obedient.</font>

338
00:22:14,550 --> 00:22:15,550
<font color="yellow">In Bong.</font>

339
00:22:16,050 --> 00:22:18,690
<font color="yellow">You can't communicate with Jacqueline.</font>

340
00:22:18,850 --> 00:22:20,250
<font color="yellow">Don't give me the money, then.</font>

341
00:22:20,350 --> 00:22:21,720
<font color="yellow">Just stop saying stupid things.</font>

342
00:22:22,050 --> 00:22:24,020
<font color="yellow">I make a fortune.</font>

343
00:22:24,120 --> 00:22:25,750
<font color="yellow">Do you think it's about that?</font>

344
00:22:25,850 --> 00:22:28,190
<font color="yellow">You'll have children to raise.</font>

345
00:22:28,290 --> 00:22:30,550
<font color="yellow">Mum and I have a lot of concerns.</font>

346
00:22:30,650 --> 00:22:31,650
<font color="yellow">You aren't well.</font>

347
00:22:32,490 --> 00:22:33,490
<font color="yellow">In Bong!</font>

348
00:23:36,950 --> 00:23:37,950
<font color="yellow">Mum.</font>

349
00:23:38,850 --> 00:23:41,550
<font color="yellow">I'm a super star.</font>

350
00:23:42,120 --> 00:23:44,650
<font color="yellow">If it's about 20,000 dollars, you should have just called.</font>

351
00:23:44,650 --> 00:23:46,590
<font color="yellow">Why would you come all the way here?</font>

352
00:23:46,590 --> 00:23:49,490
<font color="yellow">You must have transferred at least three times.</font>

353
00:23:49,950 --> 00:23:53,850
<font color="yellow">Well, you have to use your money for cancer.</font>

354
00:23:53,920 --> 00:23:55,220
<font color="yellow">Come on.</font>

355
00:23:56,690 --> 00:23:58,050
<font color="yellow">I have enough.</font>

356
00:23:59,050 --> 00:24:01,250
<font color="yellow">Also, why didn't you ask Nan Hee?</font>

357
00:24:01,490 --> 00:24:04,090
<font color="yellow">She's a boss.</font>

358
00:24:05,490 --> 00:24:08,290
<font color="yellow">Does she not give you money?</font>

359
00:24:08,690 --> 00:24:10,590
<font color="yellow">She does, but I need more.</font>

360
00:24:12,820 --> 00:24:15,320
<font color="yellow">When In Bong fell from that telegraph pole,</font>

361
00:24:16,290 --> 00:24:18,550
<font color="yellow">she worked so hard to save him.</font>

362
00:24:19,220 --> 00:24:22,050
<font color="yellow">He had 12 surgeries up to 2 years ago.</font>

363
00:24:22,750 --> 00:24:24,990
<font color="yellow">She spent more than 100 grand.</font>

364
00:24:25,450 --> 00:24:28,290
<font color="yellow">She even made herbal medicine for us every season.</font>

365
00:24:28,850 --> 00:24:31,750
<font color="yellow">On top of that, her dad goes to the emergency every now and then.</font>

366
00:24:32,290 --> 00:24:33,790
<font color="yellow">What's the point of being a boss?</font>

367
00:24:34,290 --> 00:24:36,120
<font color="yellow">We're wasting her money away.</font>

368
00:24:37,550 --> 00:24:39,090
<font color="yellow">And I can't seem to die.</font>

369
00:24:40,290 --> 00:24:42,720
<font color="yellow">Why would you die?</font>

370
00:24:45,290 --> 00:24:47,090
<font color="yellow">We're not her mum, dad or brother.</font>

371
00:24:47,750 --> 00:24:49,550
<font color="yellow">We're ghosts who steal her money.</font>

372
00:24:51,590 --> 00:24:53,750
<font color="yellow">When I die, cremate me.</font>

373
00:24:54,590 --> 00:24:56,890
<font color="yellow">You can sell our burial grounds and keep the money.</font>

374
00:24:57,590 --> 00:24:58,820
<font color="yellow">Lend me your money.</font>

375
00:25:00,320 --> 00:25:02,150
<font color="yellow">Don't tell Nan Hee.</font>

376
00:25:02,920 --> 00:25:04,750
<font color="yellow">Once she gets nephews or nieces,</font>

377
00:25:05,020 --> 00:25:06,850
<font color="yellow">Nan Hee will be responsible for them, too.</font>

378
00:25:07,590 --> 00:25:09,450
<font color="yellow">That crazy fool.</font>

379
00:25:10,490 --> 00:25:12,590
<font color="yellow">All he can think about is that girl.</font>

380
00:25:12,590 --> 00:25:13,890
<font color="yellow">He's crazy.</font>

381
00:25:15,590 --> 00:25:17,420
<font color="yellow">Oh, Mum.</font>

382
00:25:17,950 --> 00:25:19,020
<font color="yellow">Why am I...</font>

383
00:25:19,990 --> 00:25:23,290
<font color="yellow">worried about money all my life?</font>

384
00:25:26,950 --> 00:25:29,190
<font color="yellow">Mum, take my car.</font>

385
00:25:29,190 --> 00:25:30,590
<font color="yellow">I have a driver.</font>

386
00:25:31,190 --> 00:25:32,320
<font color="yellow">Go.</font>

387
00:25:32,390 --> 00:25:33,720
<font color="yellow">Drive her home.</font>

388
00:25:52,120 --> 00:25:53,920
<font color="yellow">Where's the eye?</font>

389
00:26:02,090 --> 00:26:05,150
<font color="yellow">Good. The eye is the best part.</font>

390
00:26:06,020 --> 00:26:08,250
<font color="yellow">Sure. It's the best.</font>

391
00:26:13,290 --> 00:26:14,290
<font color="yellow">Why are you so nice?</font>

392
00:26:16,020 --> 00:26:18,150
<font color="yellow">I nagged at you to clean the fridge...</font>

393
00:26:18,150 --> 00:26:19,420
<font color="yellow">and now, you finally did.</font>

394
00:26:19,650 --> 00:26:20,720
<font color="yellow">I'm trying to be nice.</font>

395
00:26:21,190 --> 00:26:22,190
<font color="yellow">Why?</font>

396
00:26:23,690 --> 00:26:25,150
<font color="yellow">We don't have much time left.</font>

397
00:26:26,550 --> 00:26:29,450
<font color="yellow">You're finally getting mature.</font>

398
00:26:29,850 --> 00:26:30,990
<font color="yellow">Good thinking.</font>

399
00:26:31,290 --> 00:26:32,920
<font color="yellow">We won't live that long.</font>

400
00:26:32,920 --> 00:26:34,690
<font color="yellow">Let's be nice to each other.</font>

401
00:26:34,850 --> 00:26:36,320
<font color="yellow">That's the best for a couple.</font>

402
00:26:37,950 --> 00:26:39,850
<font color="yellow">Why aren't you eating?</font>

403
00:26:40,120 --> 00:26:41,650
<font color="yellow">To save you money.</font>

404
00:26:41,820 --> 00:26:44,190
<font color="yellow">Great. You can lose weight, too.</font>

405
00:26:49,890 --> 00:26:50,920
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

406
00:26:51,850 --> 00:26:53,220
<font color="yellow">Yes, I called.</font>

407
00:26:53,990 --> 00:26:54,990
<font color="yellow">Hold on.</font>

408
00:27:02,220 --> 00:27:04,150
<font color="yellow">Have this after you're done.</font>

409
00:27:04,190 --> 00:27:05,390
<font color="yellow">It's good for you.</font>

410
00:27:13,390 --> 00:27:14,850
<font color="yellow">I guess I'll live another 30 years.</font>

411
00:27:15,890 --> 00:27:17,820
<font color="yellow">Why are you asking me whom I'm with?</font>

412
00:27:19,120 --> 00:27:21,390
<font color="yellow">I'm with the professors, of course. Why do you ask?</font>

413
00:27:22,090 --> 00:27:23,920
<font color="yellow">What do you think I'm doing? We're having wine.</font>

414
00:27:23,920 --> 00:27:25,320
<font color="yellow">Great.</font>

415
00:27:25,320 --> 00:27:27,820
<font color="yellow">You're having wine with young men.</font>

416
00:27:27,820 --> 00:27:30,350
<font color="yellow">Hee Ja is making rosaries alone at home.</font>

417
00:27:30,390 --> 00:27:31,790
<font color="yellow">Hee Ja has you.</font>

418
00:27:31,950 --> 00:27:33,950
<font color="yellow">Do you still have feelings for Seong Jae?</font>

419
00:27:35,950 --> 00:27:37,090
<font color="yellow">What if I do?</font>

420
00:27:37,120 --> 00:27:38,520
<font color="yellow">You need to end it.</font>

421
00:27:38,820 --> 00:27:42,220
<font color="yellow">They like each other. It makes sense for you to give up.</font>

422
00:27:43,890 --> 00:27:44,920
<font color="yellow">Why?</font>

423
00:27:45,490 --> 00:27:49,250
<font color="yellow">Let Hee Ja hang out with Seong Jae.</font>

424
00:27:49,650 --> 00:27:52,190
<font color="yellow">I go out while taking care of my kids' places.</font>

425
00:27:52,190 --> 00:27:55,020
<font color="yellow">You also have your nephews while working at the cafe.</font>

426
00:27:55,050 --> 00:27:57,150
<font color="yellow">You even have friends to drink wine with.</font>

427
00:27:57,890 --> 00:28:01,750
<font color="yellow">But all Hee Ja does is watch television at home.</font>

428
00:28:02,090 --> 00:28:04,690
<font color="yellow">She talks to herself so that she doesn't lose it.</font>

429
00:28:04,950 --> 00:28:06,820
<font color="yellow">She must have been so bored...</font>

430
00:28:06,850 --> 00:28:10,420
<font color="yellow">to make 100 rosaries in four days. Even young people can't do that.</font>

