00:28:11,320 --> 00:28:12,390
<font color="yellow">She has talent.</font>

432
00:28:12,950 --> 00:28:14,150
<font color="yellow">Won't you let her have him?</font>

433
00:28:16,820 --> 00:28:18,790
<font color="yellow">Are you upset because I'm asking you this?</font>

434
00:28:21,290 --> 00:28:23,020
<font color="yellow">You should meet Seong Jae...</font>

435
00:28:23,490 --> 00:28:25,090
<font color="yellow">in your next life.</font>

436
00:28:25,090 --> 00:28:27,720
<font color="yellow">He'll see her again in my next life.</font>

437
00:28:27,890 --> 00:28:30,450
<font color="yellow">Forget it. You should worry about your divorce.</font>

438
00:28:31,490 --> 00:28:34,820
<font color="yellow">Romance</font>

439
00:28:35,190 --> 00:28:38,290
<font color="yellow">For romance</font>

440
00:28:38,290 --> 00:28:40,550
<font color="yellow">- Welcome back. - Are you here?</font>

441
00:28:45,090 --> 00:28:46,090
<font color="yellow">Accounting book.</font>

442
00:29:02,120 --> 00:29:04,250
<font color="yellow">You have all the receipts.</font>

443
00:29:05,550 --> 00:29:07,990
<font color="yellow">This is for the burgers I had with Hee Ja last week.</font>

444
00:29:08,220 --> 00:29:09,220
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

445
00:29:22,590 --> 00:29:24,390
<font color="yellow">Come on.</font>

446
00:29:27,020 --> 00:29:30,090
<font color="yellow">Thank you for buying my work.</font>

447
00:29:30,290 --> 00:29:33,320
<font color="yellow">I'm sure it'll be worth a lot in time.</font>

448
00:29:33,320 --> 00:29:36,050
<font color="yellow">At the ceramics competition last month...</font>

449
00:29:36,050 --> 00:29:38,850
<font color="yellow">I know it won grand prize, but it's not that great.</font>

450
00:29:38,850 --> 00:29:41,190
<font color="yellow">I prefer the one you gave me as a gift last time.</font>

451
00:29:41,190 --> 00:29:44,690
<font color="yellow">You don't know how happy I am to have you as a friend.</font>

452
00:29:44,690 --> 00:29:46,220
<font color="yellow">A friend?</font>

453
00:29:47,490 --> 00:29:49,590
<font color="yellow">Be careful whom you call a friend.</font>

454
00:29:50,020 --> 00:29:51,350
<font color="yellow">For me, a friend...</font>

455
00:29:52,390 --> 00:29:53,990
<font color="yellow">is someone I can give up my lover to.</font>

456
00:29:55,550 --> 00:29:56,550
<font color="yellow">A lover?</font>

457
00:29:57,190 --> 00:29:58,590
<font color="yellow">I would've put up a fight had I been young.</font>

458
00:29:59,490 --> 00:30:02,450
<font color="yellow">I decided to give him to her, who's older than me.</font>

459
00:30:03,090 --> 00:30:07,090
<font color="yellow">Wow. If she's older than you, how old is she?</font>

460
00:30:07,090 --> 00:30:08,350
<font color="yellow">Can she even walk?</font>

461
00:30:10,890 --> 00:30:12,920
<font color="yellow">I'll pay for the taxi.</font>

462
00:30:12,950 --> 00:30:13,950
<font color="yellow">Bye, now.</font>

463
00:30:18,290 --> 00:30:19,420
<font color="yellow">It's me.</font>

464
00:30:19,550 --> 00:30:21,450
<font color="yellow">Your young friend, Choong Nam.</font>

465
00:31:03,490 --> 00:31:06,590
<font color="yellow">You cleaned the place spotless,</font>

466
00:31:06,690 --> 00:31:09,090
<font color="yellow">but your place is always dirty.</font>

467
00:31:09,490 --> 00:31:12,390
<font color="yellow">What's the occasion? You never do this.</font>

468
00:31:13,690 --> 00:31:16,820
<font color="yellow">What do you mean? I used to do this when I was young.</font>

469
00:31:17,990 --> 00:31:19,020
<font color="yellow">Don't you remember?</font>

470
00:31:19,490 --> 00:31:22,720
<font color="yellow">I used to clean my room and do the dishes since I was six.</font>

471
00:31:23,120 --> 00:31:27,250
<font color="yellow">I would even pick flowers so that you would smile.</font>

472
00:31:27,590 --> 00:31:31,290
<font color="yellow">I used to do anything that would please you.</font>

473
00:31:31,450 --> 00:31:32,450
<font color="yellow">It was after I grew up...</font>

474
00:31:33,190 --> 00:31:34,550
<font color="yellow">that I stopped doing it.</font>

475
00:31:35,050 --> 00:31:36,450
<font color="yellow">I miss those days.</font>

476
00:31:37,050 --> 00:31:38,220
<font color="yellow">How can you miss that?</font>

477
00:31:38,590 --> 00:31:41,520
<font color="yellow">I was so nervous all the time.</font>

478
00:31:42,120 --> 00:31:43,620
<font color="yellow">I was scared you'd leave me...</font>

479
00:31:43,790 --> 00:31:46,050
<font color="yellow">or try to give me drugs again.</font>

480
00:31:51,020 --> 00:31:53,920
<font color="yellow">Why do you keep talking nonsense since yesterday?</font>

481
00:31:54,190 --> 00:31:56,720
<font color="yellow">Leave. I don't want to see you. Also, Dong Jin...</font>

482
00:32:08,750 --> 00:32:09,750
<font color="yellow">Mum.</font>

483
00:32:10,820 --> 00:32:12,790
<font color="yellow">Don't get involved in my life again.</font>

484
00:32:14,750 --> 00:32:16,950
<font color="yellow">What if I do? What are you going to do?</font>

485
00:32:17,290 --> 00:32:21,020
<font color="yellow">What will you do if I do get involved?</font>

486
00:32:21,190 --> 00:32:23,190
<font color="yellow">How can you look at me like that...</font>

487
00:32:23,390 --> 00:32:25,790
<font color="yellow">for telling you to stop seeing Dong Jin?</font>

488
00:32:25,820 --> 00:32:26,920
<font color="yellow">Is it that important?</font>

489
00:32:27,750 --> 00:32:30,090
<font color="yellow">Why do you think I saw him?</font>

490
00:32:30,790 --> 00:32:32,050
<font color="yellow">Is that my fault, too?</font>

491
00:32:32,220 --> 00:32:34,420
<font color="yellow">Of course. It's your fault.</font>

492
00:32:35,090 --> 00:32:36,490
<font color="yellow">I wanted to be reckless.</font>

493
00:32:37,290 --> 00:32:39,690
<font color="yellow">Why do you think I broke up with Yeon Ha after living with him?</font>

494
00:32:40,220 --> 00:32:41,920
<font color="yellow">You lived with him?</font>

495
00:32:42,190 --> 00:32:45,420
<font color="yellow">I'm yours, so I can't do anything you won't allow me to do.</font>

496
00:32:45,690 --> 00:32:47,390
<font color="yellow">You don't like the disabled, right?</font>

497
00:32:47,750 --> 00:32:49,950
<font color="yellow">That's why I left him there when he got injured.</font>

498
00:32:51,290 --> 00:32:54,290
<font color="yellow">You had a stroke then, so I had a good excuse.</font>

499
00:32:55,090 --> 00:32:58,550
<font color="yellow">When I was six, in the field by Grandma's house,</font>

500
00:32:59,520 --> 00:33:00,990
<font color="yellow">when you poisoned me.</font>

501
00:33:02,020 --> 00:33:03,590
<font color="yellow">That's when I knew it.</font>

502
00:33:04,450 --> 00:33:05,850
<font color="yellow">I belong to Mum.</font>

503
00:33:06,320 --> 00:33:07,320
<font color="yellow">So...</font>

504
00:33:08,390 --> 00:33:11,450
<font color="yellow">even though I'm scared, if she tells me to drink,</font>

505
00:33:12,490 --> 00:33:13,850
<font color="yellow">I must drink it.</font>

506
00:33:15,490 --> 00:33:18,950
<font color="yellow">It's your fault that I left Yeon Ha.</font>

507
00:33:20,090 --> 00:33:22,020
<font color="yellow">I loved him more than anything,</font>

508
00:33:22,790 --> 00:33:26,660
<font color="yellow">and once I left him, my inner voice said,</font>

509
00:33:26,990 --> 00:33:27,990
<font color="yellow">"You cruel witch."</font>

510
00:33:29,050 --> 00:33:30,320
<font color="yellow">"Live however you want."</font>

511
00:33:30,890 --> 00:33:32,050
<font color="yellow">"Forget about your conscience."</font>

512
00:33:34,090 --> 00:33:35,390
<font color="yellow">"Waste your life away."</font>

513
00:33:39,320 --> 00:33:40,820
<font color="yellow">Say you're sorry.</font>

514
00:33:43,850 --> 00:33:45,720
<font color="yellow">Say you're sorry!</font>

515
00:33:48,950 --> 00:33:50,160
<font color="yellow">Why did you do it?</font>

516
00:33:50,820 --> 00:33:53,490
<font color="yellow">Am I yours? Just because you had me,</font>

517
00:33:54,050 --> 00:33:55,450
<font color="yellow">does it mean you can kill me?</font>

518
00:33:58,690 --> 00:33:59,950
<font color="yellow">Why did you do it?</font>

519
00:34:01,220 --> 00:34:03,550
<font color="yellow">Why am I yours? Tell me.</font>

520
00:34:06,290 --> 00:34:08,020
<font color="yellow">Tell me why you did it.</font>

521
00:34:08,190 --> 00:34:11,520
<font color="yellow">Why am I yours? Why am I yours?</font>

522
00:34:12,820 --> 00:34:15,520
<font color="yellow">Tell me! Why am I yours?</font>

523
00:34:17,090 --> 00:34:18,320
<font color="yellow">Tell me.</font>

524
00:34:18,350 --> 00:34:21,160
<font color="yellow">Of course, you are mine.</font>

525
00:34:21,160 --> 00:34:24,490
<font color="yellow">Let go. Let me go! Let go of me!</font>

526
00:34:25,250 --> 00:34:28,890
<font color="yellow">I hate it! I hate you so much!</font>

527
00:34:29,190 --> 00:34:32,690
<font color="yellow">I wanted to die and couldn't leave you behind.</font>

528
00:34:33,020 --> 00:34:34,690
<font color="yellow">How could I?</font>

529
00:34:45,790 --> 00:34:48,750
<font color="yellow">- Stop it! - Die! Die!</font>

530
00:34:49,450 --> 00:34:51,490
<font color="yellow">Die. Die!</font>

531
00:34:54,690 --> 00:34:57,190
<font color="yellow">Die! Just die!</font>

532
00:35:06,250 --> 00:35:08,720
<font color="yellow">Let go of me. I hate you!</font>

533
00:35:09,090 --> 00:35:12,120
<font color="yellow">Please stop it. You can hate me.</font>

534
00:35:12,250 --> 00:35:14,020
<font color="yellow">Now, I know everything.</font>

535
00:35:14,490 --> 00:35:16,850
<font color="yellow">You can hate me. I don't mind.</font>

536
00:35:16,850 --> 00:35:18,990
<font color="yellow">- Just don't do this. - Let go. Let me go.</font>

537
00:35:18,990 --> 00:35:20,990
<font color="yellow">Please don't do this, Wan.</font>

538
00:35:20,990 --> 00:35:22,890
<font color="yellow">Let me go!</font>

539
00:35:22,990 --> 00:35:24,720
<font color="yellow">Wan, please...</font>

540
00:35:29,720 --> 00:35:31,390
<font color="yellow">Wan! Wan!</font>

541
00:35:31,660 --> 00:35:32,720
<font color="yellow">Dad!</font>

542
00:35:47,520 --> 00:35:49,390
<font color="yellow">You're a coward, Wan.</font>

543
00:35:50,250 --> 00:35:52,660
<font color="yellow">Why did you bring up a 30-year-old story...</font>

544
00:35:52,990 --> 00:35:55,690
<font color="yellow">only to speak of it like a lunatic?</font>

545
00:35:57,050 --> 00:36:00,950
<font color="yellow">You understood your mum then as you do now.</font>

546
00:36:01,660 --> 00:36:05,020
<font color="yellow">So why do you blame her so much?</font>

547
00:36:08,550 --> 00:36:09,820
<font color="yellow">You're the reason...</font>

548
00:36:09,990 --> 00:36:12,660
<font color="yellow">I'm like this and broke up with Yeon Ha.</font>

549
00:36:12,920 --> 00:36:15,890
<font color="yellow">I'm like this because of you!</font>

550
00:36:16,220 --> 00:36:18,890
<font color="yellow">You're bleeding. Stop it, please.</font>

551
00:36:19,190 --> 00:36:20,290
<font color="yellow">I knew it then.</font>

552
00:36:20,290 --> 00:36:21,660
<font color="yellow">I'm sick of this.</font>

553
00:36:21,660 --> 00:36:24,790
<font color="yellow">I couldn't forgive myself for leaving Yeon Ha.</font>

554
00:36:25,350 --> 00:36:28,890
<font color="yellow">I wanted an excuse so that I didn't have to say I left him...</font>

555
00:36:30,160 --> 00:36:32,590
<font color="yellow">purely out of my own selfishness.</font>

556
00:36:40,490 --> 00:36:43,020
<font color="yellow">It was too hard to shoulder the blame.</font>

557
00:36:43,490 --> 00:36:45,050
<font color="yellow">So I wanted to blame another.</font>

558
00:36:46,020 --> 00:36:49,790
<font color="yellow">And the easiest and closest victim was my mum.</font>

559
00:36:49,790 --> 00:36:51,750
<font color="yellow">Stop doing this.</font>

560
00:36:51,750 --> 00:36:53,750
<font color="yellow">Let go of me!</font>

561
00:36:53,820 --> 00:36:54,890
<font color="yellow">Wan, stop.</font>

562
00:36:54,890 --> 00:36:57,050
<font color="yellow">I missed Yeon Ha so much.</font>

563
00:37:10,520 --> 00:37:12,250
<font color="yellow">Japchae with noodles?</font>

564
00:37:12,850 --> 00:37:14,620
<font color="yellow">That doesn't make sense.</font>

565
00:37:15,090 --> 00:37:16,660
<font color="yellow">Just have a bite.</font>

566
00:37:16,660 --> 00:37:19,090
<font color="yellow">You made way too much.</font>

567
00:37:25,350 --> 00:37:26,550
<font color="yellow">It's good.</font>

568
00:37:27,990 --> 00:37:30,320
<font color="yellow">I can't eat any more.</font>

569
00:37:30,390 --> 00:37:32,050
<font color="yellow">Give it to your son.</font>

570
00:37:32,190 --> 00:37:33,490
<font color="yellow">I don't do that.</font>

571
00:37:34,050 --> 00:37:37,390
<font color="yellow">It's best for everyone if we see less of each other.</font>

572
00:37:37,450 --> 00:37:39,120
<font color="yellow">They don't like me bringing food.</font>

573
00:37:39,120 --> 00:37:41,120
<font color="yellow">Then freeze it and send it.</font>

574
00:37:41,120 --> 00:37:43,820
<font color="yellow">I heard they don't like unwanted parcels.</font>

575
00:37:43,920 --> 00:37:44,920
<font color="yellow">Why?</font>

576
00:37:44,920 --> 00:37:46,950
<font color="yellow">In case their parents are inside it.</font>

577
00:37:48,850 --> 00:37:50,490
<font color="yellow">Did you make that up?</font>

578
00:37:50,520 --> 00:37:51,990
<font color="yellow">I understand.</font>

579
00:37:52,390 --> 00:37:55,720
<font color="yellow">Life for people their age is so tough.</font>

580
00:37:56,250 --> 00:37:57,490
<font color="yellow">It gives them headaches.</font>

581
00:37:58,550 --> 00:38:00,220
<font color="yellow">They regret it after their parents die.</font>

582
00:38:00,220 --> 00:38:01,920
<font color="yellow">And use guilt to call it even.</font>

583
00:38:03,850 --> 00:38:05,420
<font color="yellow">They're so cunning.</font>

584
00:38:13,850 --> 00:38:15,020
<font color="yellow">Seong Jae.</font>

585
00:38:15,690 --> 00:38:19,520
<font color="yellow">Bring your car over to Hee Ja's and take her somewhere.</font>

586
00:38:19,660 --> 00:38:20,720
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

587
00:38:23,050 --> 00:38:24,820
<font color="yellow">- What? - Didn't you hear me?</font>

588
00:38:25,290 --> 00:38:26,490
<font color="yellow">Then forget it.</font>

589
00:38:27,750 --> 00:38:29,160
<font color="yellow">What was that about?</font>

590
00:38:29,390 --> 00:38:31,750
<font color="yellow">I'm letting you have him.</font>

591
00:38:35,190 --> 00:38:36,950
<font color="yellow">Thank you, Choong Nam.</font>

592
00:38:39,050 --> 00:38:40,320
<font color="yellow">No thanks.</font>

593
00:38:41,520 --> 00:38:44,220
<font color="yellow">You were going to go travelling. Were you flirting?</font>

594
00:38:44,220 --> 00:38:46,490
<font color="yellow">That was just a split-second...</font>

595
00:38:47,820 --> 00:38:48,820
<font color="yellow">Wait.</font>

596
00:38:50,050 --> 00:38:51,620
<font color="yellow">I'm too old for that.</font>

597
00:38:51,850 --> 00:38:54,890
<font color="yellow">It's weird if people our age go on a date.</font>

598
00:38:55,290 --> 00:38:57,290
<font color="yellow">At our age, it's very possible...</font>

599
00:38:57,290 --> 00:39:01,020
<font color="yellow">that one of us could keel over and die mid-meal.</font>

600
00:39:01,160 --> 00:39:04,720
<font color="yellow">People our age can go travelling if they want to.</font>

601
00:39:04,720 --> 00:39:07,590
<font color="yellow">We could die of something at any moment.</font>

602
00:39:07,590 --> 00:39:09,920
<font color="yellow">What's so strange about going on a date?</font>

603
00:39:10,050 --> 00:39:11,720
<font color="yellow">What's wrong with a trip?</font>

604
00:39:11,790 --> 00:39:15,290
<font color="yellow">Burn the last of your embers before you fade away.</font>

605
00:39:15,520 --> 00:39:17,120
<font color="yellow">It's totally understandable.</font>

606
00:39:17,920 --> 00:39:18,920
<font color="yellow">Is it?</font>

607
00:39:20,950 --> 00:39:23,690
<font color="yellow">But you said you like him.</font>

608
00:39:23,820 --> 00:39:26,720
<font color="yellow">Not any more. He said he likes you.</font>

609
00:39:27,160 --> 00:39:29,220
<font color="yellow">I fell out of love for him that instant.</font>

610
00:39:30,450 --> 00:39:31,550
<font color="yellow">It's true.</font>

611
00:39:33,660 --> 00:39:35,590
<font color="yellow">You need to pack for your trip.</font>

612
00:39:36,620 --> 00:39:37,660
<font color="yellow">Let me see.</font>

613
00:39:38,490 --> 00:39:39,920
<font color="yellow">Take these.</font>

614
00:39:41,420 --> 00:39:42,620
<font color="yellow">They're facial masks.</font>

615
00:39:43,920 --> 00:39:45,350
<font color="yellow">Do you want to join us?</font>

616
00:39:45,590 --> 00:39:47,750
<font color="yellow">That would be even weirder than if...</font>

617
00:39:48,090 --> 00:39:52,550
<font color="yellow">the both of us ended up drowning in a saucer full of water.</font>

618
00:39:58,820 --> 00:40:00,160
<font color="yellow">Are you eloping?</font>

619
00:40:05,490 --> 00:40:07,450
<font color="yellow">In case of low blood sugar.</font>

620
00:40:08,750 --> 00:40:10,520
<font color="yellow">Take half this much.</font>

621
00:40:14,450 --> 00:40:16,350
<font color="yellow">What are these?</font>

622
00:40:16,520 --> 00:40:18,550
<font color="yellow">I'm incontinent.</font>

623
00:40:18,890 --> 00:40:20,950
<font color="yellow">- Adult diapers? - Move on.</font>

624
00:40:22,590 --> 00:40:24,790
<font color="yellow">We wore these as babies...</font>

625
00:40:25,420 --> 00:40:27,450
<font color="yellow">and again as old people.</font>

626
00:40:27,720 --> 00:40:29,790
<font color="yellow">Life really blows.</font>

627
00:40:32,990 --> 00:40:35,020
<font color="yellow">I need those.</font>

628
00:40:35,120 --> 00:40:39,490
<font color="yellow">Forget it. Tell Seong Jae that you need to pee every hour.</font>

629
00:40:39,490 --> 00:40:41,250
<font color="yellow">Tell him that's what girls do.</font>

630
00:40:41,250 --> 00:40:43,690
<font color="yellow">If he refuses to stop the car every hour,</font>

631
00:40:43,690 --> 00:40:45,350
<font color="yellow">call it quits and come home.</font>

632
00:40:45,350 --> 00:40:48,890
<font color="yellow">I still think I'll need those.</font>

633
00:40:48,890 --> 00:40:51,690
<font color="yellow">Even the gentlemanly Seong Jae will laugh at you.</font>

634
00:40:52,390 --> 00:40:55,550
<font color="yellow">"Hee Ja, I'll carry that for you."</font>

635
00:40:55,750 --> 00:40:58,990
<font color="yellow">Then he'll wonder why the bag is so light.</font>

636
00:40:59,050 --> 00:41:03,020
<font color="yellow">When you aren't around, he will open it up.</font>

637
00:41:03,850 --> 00:41:07,690
<font color="yellow">He'll be shocked if he saw half a bag full of diapers.</font>

638
00:41:07,850 --> 00:41:09,950
<font color="yellow">This is why I don't want to go anywhere.</font>

639
00:41:09,950 --> 00:41:13,420
<font color="yellow">Even for a short trip, I have to pack so much.</font>

640
00:41:13,720 --> 00:41:14,890
<font color="yellow">It's such a bother.</font>

641
00:41:16,820 --> 00:41:20,420
<font color="yellow">At least you can still walk. Think positively.</font>

642
00:41:21,890 --> 00:41:24,920
<font color="yellow">Do you always sleep out here?</font>

